WEBVTT

01:32.110 --> 01:34.930
[How dare you!?]

01:35.030 --> 01:39.920
[Episode 23]

01:41.680 --> 01:42.280
Lord Chen.

01:42.479 --> 01:43.000
Please.

01:44.120 --> 01:44.789
Lord Chen.

01:47.039 --> 01:47.640
Good morning, Lord Chen.

01:47.640 --> 01:48.039
Hello.

01:49.070 --> 01:50.590
So many new faces around.

01:50.870 --> 01:52.400
Indeed. We thought
when the Empress Dowager fell,

01:52.400 --> 01:53.460
we'd be in trouble.

01:53.759 --> 01:55.710
But unexpectedly,
we've risen to prominence.

01:55.710 --> 01:57.570
Now we're riding high on success.

01:57.870 --> 02:00.130
I haven't been sleeping well these days,

02:00.280 --> 02:01.000
afraid

02:01.230 --> 02:02.950
it's all just a fleeting dream.

02:02.950 --> 02:03.310
Lord Chen.

02:03.310 --> 02:04.560
Don't you get it yet?

02:05.040 --> 02:07.240
We thought Prince Duan was formidable,

02:07.400 --> 02:08.590
but now we realize

02:09.080 --> 02:10.280
the more ruthless one

02:10.479 --> 02:11.600
is above him.

02:12.000 --> 02:13.080
Lord Chen is right.

02:13.800 --> 02:16.000
Who gets promoted
and who loses their life—

02:16.000 --> 02:17.590
it's all within

02:18.030 --> 02:19.360
the Emperor's control.

02:20.800 --> 02:21.460
Do you think

02:21.870 --> 02:23.280
His Majesty will seek to

02:23.560 --> 02:24.910
settle scores with us later?

02:24.910 --> 02:26.310
What scores would there be?

02:26.310 --> 02:28.970
The Emperor
and the Empress Dowager are family.

02:29.190 --> 02:31.160
All these years, we've diligently

02:31.190 --> 02:32.910
served His Majesty.

02:33.750 --> 02:35.590
If anyone would have scores to be settled,

02:35.590 --> 02:36.520
it should be

02:37.680 --> 02:38.880
the other faction's.

02:41.780 --> 02:42.710
Did you see that?

02:43.440 --> 02:45.600
They avoid us like the plague.

02:46.870 --> 02:48.960
A bunch of opportunists.

02:50.110 --> 02:52.460
His Highness hasn't summoned us for days.

02:53.160 --> 02:54.760
What should we do?

02:55.310 --> 02:56.970
We're completely in the dark.

02:57.490 --> 02:59.220
It's better not to be summoned.

02:59.430 --> 03:01.830
His Majesty is displeased with us now.

03:02.410 --> 03:04.350
This is for our protection.

03:05.740 --> 03:06.740
That's not right.

03:06.900 --> 03:09.960
I saw Lord Mu
enter the Emperor's residence yesterday.

03:17.950 --> 03:21.110
His Majesty arrives!

03:24.530 --> 03:26.740
Long live Your Majesty!

03:32.060 --> 03:33.120
Rise, all of you.

03:33.460 --> 03:35.280
Thank you, Your Majesty.

03:38.820 --> 03:39.750
Where is Lord Mu?

03:42.630 --> 03:43.430
Your Majesty,

03:43.930 --> 03:44.970
I am here.

03:45.570 --> 03:47.100
The personnel evaluation records

03:47.100 --> 03:48.930
of the Ministry of Personnel

03:49.610 --> 03:51.750
that I ordered you to submit—
why aren't they completed yet?

03:51.750 --> 03:52.550
Your Majesty,

03:53.450 --> 03:54.570
over the past decade,

03:54.570 --> 03:57.120
the changes in the court officials
have been complex.

03:57.120 --> 04:00.070
The recording work
is enormous and tedious.

04:00.560 --> 04:02.720
It cannot be completed overnight.

04:03.370 --> 04:05.030
I humbly request Your Majesty

04:05.100 --> 04:06.750
to grant me a few more days.

04:07.100 --> 04:09.070
These personnel evaluations

04:09.100 --> 04:10.870
should be organized annually.

04:11.940 --> 04:13.000
Isn't tracking changes

04:13.000 --> 04:14.480
a simple matter?

04:15.130 --> 04:16.779
Look at our Ministry of Revenue.

04:16.779 --> 04:18.250
The changes we have to track

04:18.250 --> 04:21.170
are the changes in land and population
across the country.

04:21.170 --> 04:23.570
The workload is hundreds of times greater,

04:24.060 --> 04:25.800
yet we still completed it.

04:26.000 --> 04:27.090
That's right.

04:27.140 --> 04:28.140
Indeed.

04:28.780 --> 04:29.570
Exactly.

04:29.660 --> 04:30.460
Your Majesty,

04:31.460 --> 04:34.780
recently, there have been
frequent personnel changes in court.

04:34.780 --> 04:35.980
In my ministry alone,

04:36.610 --> 04:38.490
including the Left Vice Minister,

04:38.490 --> 04:40.490
we are short five officials.

04:41.020 --> 04:42.820
I have been searching for

04:42.900 --> 04:45.500
suitable candidates
to fill these positions.

04:46.659 --> 04:48.150
But unfortunately...

04:49.460 --> 04:50.260
Your Majesty.

04:53.700 --> 04:55.150
I do not agree

04:55.850 --> 04:56.409
with

04:57.140 --> 04:58.310
Lord Mu.

05:00.100 --> 05:01.050
If we're talking about

05:01.050 --> 05:03.170
having difficulty looking for candidates,

05:03.170 --> 05:05.020
it's obvious that the Ministry of War

05:05.020 --> 05:06.710
has it the most difficult.

05:07.580 --> 05:10.840
Although the court
has suffered serious losses recently,

05:10.900 --> 05:13.700
many talented
young officials have emerged.

05:14.970 --> 05:15.730
Lord Mu,

05:16.520 --> 05:18.130
why not promote them?

05:18.340 --> 05:21.670
Lord Mu, you mustn't
let your personal feelings interfere.

05:22.280 --> 05:23.610
Your Majesty, you are wise!

05:23.610 --> 05:25.780
I... I would never dare do such a thing!

05:27.810 --> 05:29.850
My ministers, you all make valid points.

05:29.850 --> 05:30.980
I can understand

05:31.460 --> 05:33.060
Lord Mu's difficulties too.

05:33.970 --> 05:35.830
But this matter must be resolved.

05:36.930 --> 05:37.790
How about this?

05:39.140 --> 05:41.200
Is there anyone willing to volunteer

05:41.250 --> 05:43.450
to help Lord Mu with this urgent matter?

05:48.820 --> 05:49.360
I,

05:49.850 --> 05:50.940
Yang Duojie!

05:55.780 --> 05:57.570
Am willing to help Lord Mu.

05:58.420 --> 06:01.700
Isn't this Lord Yang
from the Imperial Astronomer's office?

06:01.700 --> 06:03.050
The Imperial Astronomer's office

06:03.050 --> 06:05.780
has nothing to do
with the Ministry of Personnel.

06:07.290 --> 06:07.850
Your Majesty...

06:07.850 --> 06:09.050
Is this appropriate?

06:09.620 --> 06:12.020
Since I joined
the Imperial Astronomer's office,

06:12.020 --> 06:13.290
I've calculated calendars,

06:13.290 --> 06:14.730
established seasonal divisions,

06:14.730 --> 06:16.100
observed celestial phenomena,

06:16.100 --> 06:17.290
and divined fortunes.

06:17.290 --> 06:18.310
All these duties

06:18.900 --> 06:20.830
require coordination and cooperation

06:20.830 --> 06:22.020
with various ministries

06:22.020 --> 06:24.650
and attention to every detail.

06:25.460 --> 06:26.120
Therefore,

06:27.050 --> 06:28.810
I think I am

06:30.460 --> 06:32.450
the best candidate

06:33.650 --> 06:34.840
to extend help

06:35.900 --> 06:37.490
to Lord Mu.

06:40.970 --> 06:43.370
Lord Yang previously saved us
at Mount Bei,

06:43.640 --> 06:46.420
and now takes the initiative to help
the Ministry of Personnel—

06:46.420 --> 06:49.010
he is truly a talented young official!

06:50.020 --> 06:53.080
If my Ministry of Revenue
weren't running so smoothly,

06:53.150 --> 06:55.180
I would want to ask Lord Mu

06:55.530 --> 06:56.800
to transfer him to me.

06:58.690 --> 06:59.610
Indeed!

06:59.790 --> 07:01.160
I second that.

07:01.980 --> 07:04.180
-I also agree.
-I also agree.

07:04.900 --> 07:05.960
If that's the case,

07:07.600 --> 07:09.840
I promote Yang Duojie
to Vice Minister of Personnel

07:09.840 --> 07:11.970
to quickly compile the records I need.

07:15.270 --> 07:16.550
As for Lord Mu...

07:18.010 --> 07:18.810
Your Majesty.

07:19.290 --> 07:21.020
You've been overworked lately.

07:21.020 --> 07:22.100
You should rest

07:22.450 --> 07:23.410
at home for now.

07:45.700 --> 07:46.560
Your Highness.

07:47.250 --> 07:48.210
By all accounts,

07:48.810 --> 07:51.580
I'm openly aligned
with the Empress Dowager's faction.

07:51.580 --> 07:53.400
Yet he not only
doesn't try to win me over,

07:53.400 --> 07:56.780
but puts me on the hot seat repeatedly.

07:57.730 --> 07:59.460
I've been thinking hard,

07:59.850 --> 08:02.450
but I don't think
I've shown any flaw anywhere.

08:03.290 --> 08:05.290
Please understand, Your Highness.

08:05.570 --> 08:07.170
Lord Mu, you misunderstand.

08:08.470 --> 08:10.210
I don't mean to blame you.

08:10.760 --> 08:13.490
This is just like
the recent failure at Mount Bei.

08:13.490 --> 08:14.540
We know for sure

08:15.120 --> 08:16.450
the strategy was sound,

08:17.500 --> 08:20.160
but there were just
some unexpected variables.

08:23.700 --> 08:24.410
Variables?

08:25.940 --> 08:26.710
The first one

08:27.690 --> 08:29.850
is the strange firearms they possess.

08:30.500 --> 08:32.630
Its destructive power is terrifying.

08:32.710 --> 08:33.570
The other one is

08:35.190 --> 08:37.600
that the expert we met
on the pleasure boat

08:39.780 --> 08:41.169
is not dead.

08:42.720 --> 08:44.500
Noble Consort Yu deceived us?

08:54.280 --> 08:55.610
Even if she deceived us,

08:56.730 --> 08:58.660
if no one had tipped them off

09:00.690 --> 09:02.710
and handed over our undercover agents,

09:02.710 --> 09:04.040
along with Lord Murong,

09:04.350 --> 09:05.920
as gifts of surrender,

09:07.090 --> 09:08.290
I believe the Emperor

09:08.890 --> 09:11.290
wouldn't have made it down
Mount Bei alive.

09:12.970 --> 09:15.570
The one who knew
the entire assassination plan

09:16.370 --> 09:19.110
and was aware
of all the personnel involved...

09:21.620 --> 09:22.670
It's Consort Xie!

09:30.590 --> 09:32.300
That wretched woman...

09:35.890 --> 09:37.120
Hot pot?

09:37.610 --> 09:39.000
Two soup bases too!

09:39.460 --> 09:40.600
We've been waiting for you.

09:40.600 --> 09:41.400
Come sit down.

09:41.580 --> 09:43.840
If I'd known you lived like this,

09:43.980 --> 09:45.650
I would've switched factions long ago.

09:45.650 --> 09:47.160
It's not too late now.

09:47.300 --> 09:48.370
After we finish eating,

09:48.370 --> 09:49.770
let's play some mahjong.

09:51.150 --> 09:51.950
You know what?

09:52.210 --> 09:53.420
Rumors are spreading among the people

09:53.420 --> 09:53.850
saying

09:54.720 --> 09:56.030
I harmed the Empress Dowager.

09:56.030 --> 09:57.290
And that thunderstorm

09:57.300 --> 10:00.100
was divine punishment
for my misconduct as ruler.

10:01.240 --> 10:01.840
Eat this.

10:02.820 --> 10:05.220
This is clearly a rumor
spread by Prince Duan's faction.

10:05.220 --> 10:07.550
Prince Duan values
having a legitimate cause.

10:07.550 --> 10:08.420
Those rumors

10:08.950 --> 10:11.480
are all groundwork
for his future rebellion.

10:13.350 --> 10:14.950
Put it in the spicy soup base?

10:15.340 --> 10:18.400
But the problem is
we can't prove our innocence either.

10:19.250 --> 10:20.730
Who's spreading these rumors?

10:20.730 --> 10:21.730
I'll go kill one of them

10:21.730 --> 10:22.830
as a warning.

10:23.100 --> 10:23.960
No!

10:24.340 --> 10:25.010
Why not?

10:25.490 --> 10:27.670
Suppression will only backfire.

10:27.960 --> 10:29.220
What should we do then?

10:29.420 --> 10:31.200
Fight evil with evil!

10:31.580 --> 10:32.340
Evil?

10:33.460 --> 10:35.870
Which sect is it from?

10:35.980 --> 10:37.480
I've never heard of it.

10:39.220 --> 10:40.820
I'm from the Devil's Castle.

10:42.940 --> 10:44.040
Anyway,

10:44.530 --> 10:46.390
if Prince Duan calls you a tyrant,

10:46.580 --> 10:48.050
you call him a hypocrite.

10:48.300 --> 10:49.700
If he says you harmed the Empress Dowager,

10:49.700 --> 10:51.060
you say he hired assassins.

10:51.060 --> 10:52.370
If he says you were struck by lightning,

10:52.370 --> 10:55.180
you say as the true Son of Heaven,

10:55.200 --> 10:57.490
you can summon 81 thunderbolts
with a wave of your hand

10:57.490 --> 10:59.820
to strike down on all the other assassins.

11:00.910 --> 11:02.300
Isn't that too exaggerated?

11:02.300 --> 11:04.050
Seems quite dramatic too.

11:04.460 --> 11:06.280
What do you two know?

11:06.850 --> 11:08.050
Let me put it this way.

11:08.460 --> 11:11.060
If you excitedly share
with other people this:

11:11.480 --> 11:12.340
"Jeez!

11:12.610 --> 11:14.810
I learned something from a book today."

11:14.850 --> 11:18.330
Would you be sharing about things

11:18.370 --> 11:20.840
like the Pythagorean theorem, functions,

11:20.950 --> 11:23.100
prime numbers,
or that pi equals 3.1415926?

11:23.100 --> 11:23.980
Of course not!

11:23.980 --> 11:26.110
Because you can't even remember that.

11:26.130 --> 11:26.580
But

11:27.730 --> 11:29.290
if you go tell others,

11:29.420 --> 11:31.250
"Oh my God.

11:31.440 --> 11:32.420
That tyrant

11:32.610 --> 11:33.980
just waved his arm

11:34.370 --> 11:36.220
and summoned 100,000 thunderbolts,

11:36.220 --> 11:37.520
killing all the

11:37.650 --> 11:39.280
darn assassins."

11:40.530 --> 11:42.790
Would you go around telling others that?

11:45.730 --> 11:47.010
That makes some sense.

11:48.130 --> 11:49.630
Throughout history, Emperors,

11:49.630 --> 11:51.020
to win people's hearts,

11:51.610 --> 11:54.940
would even make up stories
about hiding books in fish bellies.

11:54.940 --> 11:56.840
The key is that
people actually believed them.

11:56.840 --> 11:58.010
Not bad, Xie.

11:58.340 --> 11:59.400
You've got skills.

12:00.110 --> 12:01.710
Prince Duan has lasted this long

12:01.710 --> 12:03.310
all because of your support.

12:05.890 --> 12:06.580
Him?

12:07.850 --> 12:08.700
That bastard.

12:09.610 --> 12:10.760
He's no fun to play with.

12:10.760 --> 12:11.760
I'm done with him.

12:13.460 --> 12:13.980
But

12:14.460 --> 12:15.520
I must warn you.

12:16.180 --> 12:18.650
Public opinion battles
are just the first wave.

12:18.650 --> 12:20.250
The real attacks come after.

12:20.420 --> 12:21.680
You better be careful.

12:22.370 --> 12:23.760
He wants legitimate reasons.

12:23.760 --> 12:25.890
He won't make a move inside the palace.

12:27.010 --> 12:27.810
That's right.

12:27.890 --> 12:29.150
Xu Yao's book also says

12:29.500 --> 12:32.300
he'll only make his move
when you leave the palace.

12:36.010 --> 12:37.610
I've been meaning to ask you.

12:38.770 --> 12:39.970
You mentioned before

12:40.100 --> 12:41.700
that the plan in Xu Yao's book

12:41.800 --> 12:43.860
was different from my original plan.

12:44.430 --> 12:45.630
How did you know that?

12:46.390 --> 12:47.920
I only told Xiahou Bo.

12:55.730 --> 12:57.220
After Xu Yao switched sides,

12:57.220 --> 12:58.420
he told me everything.

12:58.420 --> 12:59.820
He discussed all the suggestions you made

12:59.820 --> 13:01.220
with Prince Duan before.

13:03.340 --> 13:04.540
That makes sense now.

13:09.730 --> 13:10.580
I got it!

13:11.250 --> 13:11.580
What?

13:11.770 --> 13:12.770
What's wrong, Mr. Bei?

13:12.770 --> 13:13.700
What did you get?

13:13.770 --> 13:14.370
Evil!

13:27.520 --> 13:28.690
Braised egg.

13:31.690 --> 13:33.020
I didn't get that right.

13:33.570 --> 13:34.430
Let me go again.

13:36.650 --> 13:38.050
Living in ancient times,

13:38.820 --> 13:40.820
not having a bathroom heater is fine.

13:40.820 --> 13:42.060
But not having a hair dryer,

13:42.060 --> 13:43.460
that's the real trouble.

13:46.220 --> 13:47.950
Who told you to bathe every day?

13:49.850 --> 13:51.360
After hot pot, I smell all over.

13:51.360 --> 13:52.220
How can I sleep?

13:56.010 --> 13:56.740
That's true.

13:58.940 --> 13:59.940
You smell so nice.

14:00.730 --> 14:01.790
What are you doing?

14:02.560 --> 14:03.490
Let me go.

14:03.890 --> 14:04.250
No.

14:04.970 --> 14:06.300
If you keep fooling around,

14:06.300 --> 14:07.900
I'll make you take medicine.

14:07.920 --> 14:08.870
Why take medicine?

14:08.870 --> 14:09.700
I'm not sick.

14:10.540 --> 14:11.380
Quick!

14:12.250 --> 14:12.730
Let go—

14:14.370 --> 14:14.930
Quick!

14:19.850 --> 14:20.340
Mr. Bei.

14:20.730 --> 14:21.330
What is it?

14:21.940 --> 14:22.340
Dan.

14:22.530 --> 14:24.280
Li Yunxi delivered a letter.

14:40.490 --> 14:41.420
What does it say?

14:43.600 --> 14:45.800
Cen Jintian's condition has worsened.

14:46.950 --> 14:49.210
He might not make it through this winter.

14:52.580 --> 14:53.480
[For the Emperor's personal attention:
Cen Jintian's health is deteriorating.]

14:53.500 --> 14:54.540
[I'm afraid he can't make it
through winter. He has compiled]

14:54.560 --> 14:55.430
[the planting of Yan millet in a manual.]

14:55.020 --> 14:56.100
How could this be?

14:55.450 --> 14:56.390
[He hopes Your Majesty can go
see him one last time.]

14:56.770 --> 14:58.030
In the original story,

14:58.190 --> 15:00.390
he at least survived until the drought.

15:01.440 --> 15:03.300
How did it push forward by so much?

15:03.460 --> 15:04.320
That's because

15:05.460 --> 15:07.120
he was hanging on

15:07.870 --> 15:09.330
hoping to see the harvest.

15:10.970 --> 15:13.700
Now he knows the people
will survive the drought,

15:14.130 --> 15:16.260
he has nothing to worry about anymore.

15:18.180 --> 15:19.350
For him,

15:19.670 --> 15:21.130
it's a satisfying ending.

15:21.640 --> 15:23.700
How can this be considered
a happy ending?

15:23.700 --> 15:25.460
We clearly promised him before

15:25.910 --> 15:27.240
that he would live to see

15:27.340 --> 15:29.740
peace and prosperity throughout the land.

15:30.180 --> 15:30.940
But you know,

15:31.810 --> 15:34.270
when we used those words
to gain his loyalty,

15:34.530 --> 15:36.530
there probably wasn't enough time.

15:37.780 --> 15:38.640
That vision...

15:40.640 --> 15:42.040
can only remain a vision.

15:47.960 --> 15:48.790
He says

15:49.250 --> 15:51.050
he wants to see you one more time.

15:52.300 --> 15:53.900
I can't leave the palace now.

15:54.220 --> 15:54.700
I know.

15:55.340 --> 15:56.690
-So I can—
-You can't.

15:56.890 --> 15:57.620
Why not?

16:00.300 --> 16:02.160
It's too dangerous out there now.

16:02.370 --> 16:04.370
Prince Duan's spies are everywhere.

16:04.370 --> 16:05.700
I'll be careful.

16:05.730 --> 16:07.860
And I have secret guards to protect me.

16:08.090 --> 16:09.330
We lost so many men

16:09.390 --> 16:10.600
at Mount Bei.

16:11.170 --> 16:12.630
These are all we have left.

16:12.950 --> 16:14.080
And some must be sent

16:14.100 --> 16:15.430
to protect Xie Yong'er.

16:17.820 --> 16:19.100
What about Wang Zhao's funeral?

16:19.100 --> 16:20.960
Are we not attending that either?

16:22.140 --> 16:23.940
Let those scholars represent us

16:24.950 --> 16:26.580
and build a cenotaph for him.

16:27.150 --> 16:27.810
But...

16:27.870 --> 16:28.580
Wanyin.

16:29.560 --> 16:30.620
Don't forget.

16:31.220 --> 16:32.550
They are 2D characters.

16:33.980 --> 16:35.210
If you forget this,

16:36.060 --> 16:37.390
you'll be dragged down.

16:40.190 --> 16:42.350
But when you heard about Wang Zhao's death
at Mount Bei,

16:42.350 --> 16:43.880
you didn't react like this.

16:48.530 --> 16:50.130
That's why I remind myself

16:51.690 --> 16:53.560
never to get too emotional.

17:14.630 --> 17:15.359
Wanyin.

17:17.560 --> 17:19.160
You must listen to me on this.

17:21.390 --> 17:23.069
If anything happens to you,

17:25.589 --> 17:27.150
I can't go on living.

17:36.420 --> 17:37.140
By the way,

17:38.680 --> 17:40.270
your father sent a message

17:41.490 --> 17:42.950
saying he wants to see you.

17:44.660 --> 17:45.440
I guess

17:45.760 --> 17:47.760
he's not doing well with Prince Duan

17:47.920 --> 17:49.580
and sees an opportunity here.

17:49.810 --> 17:51.470
He wants to use your influence

17:51.520 --> 17:53.180
to find a new path for himself.

17:56.900 --> 17:58.100
Do you want to see him?

17:58.180 --> 17:58.760
No.

18:01.380 --> 18:02.780
As long as I don't see him,

18:03.380 --> 18:05.710
he'll forever remain just a 2D character.

18:17.770 --> 18:18.570
Your Majesty.

18:18.730 --> 18:20.700
The Ministry of Revenue's Lord Chen,
the Ministry of Personnel's Lord Liang,

18:20.700 --> 18:22.220
and the two ministers
from the Ministry of Justice

18:22.220 --> 18:23.620
have all requested leave

18:23.620 --> 18:24.180
saying

18:25.010 --> 18:27.210
they cannot come for an audience today.

18:37.010 --> 18:37.590
Die?

18:40.330 --> 18:40.860
Capture?

18:49.330 --> 18:49.880
Kill?

18:50.980 --> 18:53.660
Is Her Majesty asking for water?

18:54.220 --> 18:54.860
Water?

18:55.730 --> 18:56.540
Water, water!

18:56.770 --> 18:57.660
Quickly, get some water!

18:57.660 --> 18:58.010
Yes.

19:18.980 --> 19:19.530
Ma'am,

19:19.770 --> 19:22.100
the path is rough here. Please be careful.

19:22.350 --> 19:22.950
It's fine.

19:26.020 --> 19:26.750
Everyone,

19:27.380 --> 19:29.480
are you all my son's colleagues?

19:31.050 --> 19:33.290
We were Wang's closest friends,

19:34.140 --> 19:35.200
here to see him off.

19:36.220 --> 19:36.900
Thank you

19:37.010 --> 19:37.850
very much.

19:39.220 --> 19:40.220
My son mentioned

19:41.090 --> 19:42.940
he worked for an official

19:43.380 --> 19:44.940
who treated him very well.

19:46.010 --> 19:47.920
But I didn't know who that is.

19:48.180 --> 19:48.840
I wanted

19:49.460 --> 19:49.900
to come

19:51.460 --> 19:52.730
and thank him in person

19:53.180 --> 19:54.580
for taking care of my son.

19:59.250 --> 19:59.930
Li!

20:00.090 --> 20:01.140
Please wait a moment.

20:01.140 --> 20:01.940
Wait for what?

20:02.160 --> 20:03.940
The auspicious time you divined
is almost passing.

20:03.940 --> 20:04.400
Well...

20:11.000 --> 20:12.460
They probably won't come.

20:14.010 --> 20:15.870
There are too many eyes watching.

20:16.900 --> 20:18.330
They must be in a difficult position too.

20:18.330 --> 20:18.810
Right now,

20:18.810 --> 20:21.570
if Prince Duan's spies discover them,
it be big trouble.

20:21.570 --> 20:22.940
Her Highness usually has so many ideas.

20:22.940 --> 20:23.700
What now?

20:23.810 --> 20:24.920
She has no more ideas?

20:24.920 --> 20:26.380
Li, please don't be upset.

20:26.620 --> 20:27.980
The court is in turmoil now,

20:27.980 --> 20:29.900
and the confrontation with Prince Duan
hangs in the balance.

20:29.900 --> 20:33.010
His Majesty and Her Highness are not
the type to discard loyal servants.

20:33.010 --> 20:33.770
Right now,

20:33.900 --> 20:36.530
they must be heartbroken
that they cannot attend.

20:36.530 --> 20:38.140
If our Wang knows from the afterlife,

20:38.140 --> 20:39.740
he would surely understand.

20:42.210 --> 20:43.220
Of course I know

20:44.250 --> 20:45.620
that His Majesty and Her Highness

20:45.620 --> 20:47.080
are not heartless people.

20:47.570 --> 20:48.730
But when Wang died,

20:49.490 --> 20:50.420
he was all alone,

20:51.250 --> 20:52.650
thousands of miles away.

20:53.310 --> 20:54.250
Today at his burial,

20:54.250 --> 20:55.780
we don't even have his body,

20:55.900 --> 20:58.700
and we dare not carve his name
on the tombstone too.

20:59.350 --> 21:00.570
Yet those he trusted completely

21:00.570 --> 21:01.700
and gave his life for

21:02.620 --> 21:04.480
cannot even see him one last time.

21:05.460 --> 21:06.990
I feel it's so unfair to him.

21:07.460 --> 21:08.790
I feel such pity for him.

21:14.250 --> 21:16.410
We are here to see him off
on his final journey,

21:16.410 --> 21:17.410
so he is not alone.

21:22.940 --> 21:24.140
Where's Lord Cen?

21:27.090 --> 21:27.620
Your Highness!

21:27.620 --> 21:28.480
Your Highness!

21:31.290 --> 21:31.890
I'm sorry.

21:32.380 --> 21:33.090
I'm late.

21:33.660 --> 21:34.610
Not at all!

21:34.750 --> 21:36.460
The auspicious time hasn't passed yet.

21:36.460 --> 21:37.320
Your Highness,

21:37.320 --> 21:38.850
this is Wang Zhao's mother.

21:39.980 --> 21:42.110
Ma'am, please accept my condolences.

21:47.770 --> 21:51.290
This is the State Ceremonial Bureau Chief
court robe bestowed by His Majesty.

21:51.290 --> 21:53.980
It was meant for Lord Wang to wear
upon his return.

21:53.980 --> 21:55.290
Thank you, His Majesty.

21:55.290 --> 21:56.490
Please don't, Ma'am.

21:57.340 --> 22:00.340
What Lord Wang did
will be remembered for generations.

22:00.340 --> 22:01.540
It is our failure

22:02.360 --> 22:03.880
that we cannot publicly praise
his achievements

22:03.880 --> 22:05.610
and record his name in history.

22:15.990 --> 22:18.050
This unmarked grave in the outskirts

22:18.710 --> 22:20.310
is truly an injustice to him.

22:21.770 --> 22:23.090
My husband

22:23.700 --> 22:24.980
died in the war.

22:26.180 --> 22:28.360
Since Zhao was little, he always said

22:29.620 --> 22:30.500
when he grew up,

22:30.770 --> 22:32.770
he wanted to be a good civil official

22:33.490 --> 22:35.290
and come up with many solutions,

22:35.650 --> 22:38.310
and that we can't let people
fight wars anymore.

22:38.450 --> 22:39.080
We must

22:39.610 --> 22:41.940
bring peace and prosperity to the nation.

22:42.500 --> 22:44.440
My son...

22:45.430 --> 22:47.690
You've really done it!

22:49.400 --> 22:54.050
[State Ceremonial Bureau
Wang Zhao]

22:55.380 --> 22:57.580
With mountains and rivers as your hall,

22:59.050 --> 23:00.510
sun and moon as your torch,

23:01.700 --> 23:03.630
and plants and trees as your beams.

23:05.090 --> 23:05.650
Wang...

23:07.600 --> 23:11.990
[Tomb of the nameless]

23:08.380 --> 23:09.110
You're home.

23:16.320 --> 23:18.620
Fate willing, we'll meet in the next life.

23:18.620 --> 23:19.720
I hope then

23:20.250 --> 23:21.710
the world will be at peace,

23:22.330 --> 23:23.120
and we

23:24.010 --> 23:25.870
will serve a wise ruler together.

23:37.570 --> 23:38.730
Soul, return home.

23:40.300 --> 23:41.450
Do not journey east.

23:42.380 --> 23:44.360
The sea storms have not subsided,

23:45.480 --> 23:46.270
a lone boat

23:47.380 --> 23:48.980
cannot cross the vast ocean.

23:48.980 --> 23:50.330
Soul, return home.

23:51.290 --> 23:52.610
Do not wander west.

23:54.320 --> 23:56.250
Desert sands obscure the sun,

23:58.000 --> 24:00.820
dried bones everywhere bring sorrow.

24:03.310 --> 24:04.610
Soul, return home.

24:05.990 --> 24:07.220
Do not go south.

24:09.980 --> 24:12.240
Miasma fills the mountains and forests,

24:12.710 --> 24:15.040
and venomous snakes coil on narrow paths.

24:16.090 --> 24:17.680
Soul, return home.

24:18.570 --> 24:20.500
Do not go to the northern frontier.

24:21.490 --> 24:22.360
Ice and snow

24:23.090 --> 24:24.520
freeze the world,

24:25.730 --> 24:27.060
and the western jackdaw

24:27.570 --> 24:28.860
cries in deep sorrow.

24:29.590 --> 24:31.590
The river waters are deep and clear,

24:32.180 --> 24:34.510
and above the banks, the maple trees grow.

24:35.570 --> 24:37.430
Gaze out across a thousand miles,

24:38.660 --> 24:40.590
as I grieve by the coming of spring.

24:41.530 --> 24:42.750
Soul, return home.

24:44.090 --> 24:45.420
Soul, return home.

24:47.730 --> 24:48.930
Lament for the south.

24:50.320 --> 24:52.180
That was our only encounter.

24:53.530 --> 24:55.390
What kind of person was Wang Zhao?

24:55.740 --> 24:57.540
What were his life's ambitions?

24:57.660 --> 24:59.260
Did he have someone he loved?

25:00.010 --> 25:01.700
Before dying,
when he gazed towards Great Xia,

25:01.170 --> 25:04.720
[Tomb of the nameless]

25:01.700 --> 25:02.900
what was he thinking?

25:03.770 --> 25:04.900
I know nothing.

25:06.460 --> 25:09.660
And now all that remains
is a journey to the end of the world

25:09.770 --> 25:11.050
and an unmarked grave.

25:30.460 --> 25:31.550
Cen, I brought—

25:34.330 --> 25:35.680
Why won't you listen to me?

25:35.680 --> 25:36.740
It's so cold today.

25:40.270 --> 25:41.290
I'm fine.

25:42.530 --> 25:43.730
Her Highness is here.

25:46.290 --> 25:48.150
Please, no need for formalities.

25:50.010 --> 25:51.470
Thank you, Your Highness.

25:56.330 --> 25:57.290
Your Highness,

25:58.320 --> 26:00.650
you were able to bid
Wang a final farewell,

26:02.290 --> 26:04.290
but I couldn't.

26:05.700 --> 26:07.100
I feel deeply ashamed.

26:07.590 --> 26:08.320
Wang Zhao was

26:09.420 --> 26:11.140
free-spirited and unrestrained.

26:11.140 --> 26:14.270
I imagine he wasn't one
to care about empty formalities.

26:18.220 --> 26:19.080
Your Highness,

26:19.730 --> 26:22.860
I've documented the methods
for cultivating Yan millet

26:22.900 --> 26:25.030
in various field types in this manual.

26:26.700 --> 26:27.300
Thank you.

26:31.460 --> 26:32.860
With proper methods,

26:33.660 --> 26:34.730
it can be cultivated

26:34.730 --> 26:35.590
in forest land,

26:35.650 --> 26:36.150
[Great Xia Agriculture 9]

26:36.250 --> 26:37.250
dry land,

26:36.400 --> 26:39.000
[Sweet potatoes
have high requirements for water]

26:38.180 --> 26:38.860
as well as

26:39.000 --> 26:41.000
[Sweet potatoes prefer warm climates]

26:39.900 --> 26:40.900
paddy fields.

26:41.620 --> 26:42.950
Tu'er has promised that

26:43.050 --> 26:44.140
once he enters Yan State,

26:44.140 --> 26:46.340
he will first transport the seeds here.

26:46.720 --> 26:49.140
The Salt-for-Services Policy is also
being implemented as per usual.

26:49.140 --> 26:50.350
By next spring,

26:50.700 --> 26:52.210
farmers across the country

26:52.210 --> 26:54.010
will be able to plant Yan millet.

26:54.990 --> 26:56.700
That would be perfect.

27:02.730 --> 27:04.180
Besides planting,

27:04.750 --> 27:07.680
transportation and storage
are equally important.

27:07.860 --> 27:10.250
Yan millet is different from other grains.

27:10.250 --> 27:12.380
It needs to be dehulled before storage.

27:12.380 --> 27:13.870
With the right method,

27:14.770 --> 27:15.530
it can be

27:16.140 --> 27:17.430
preserved longer.

27:17.860 --> 27:18.360
Got it.

27:19.770 --> 27:22.010
I'll have
the Ministry of Revenue follow the manual

27:22.010 --> 27:24.340
to inspect granaries across the country.

27:24.770 --> 27:26.180
That will give us a clearer picture

27:26.180 --> 27:28.640
for future disaster relief allocation too.

27:29.660 --> 27:30.490
With that,

27:31.380 --> 27:32.980
there's only one thing left.

27:34.940 --> 27:36.090
After the drought,

27:36.810 --> 27:37.860
we still need

27:37.980 --> 27:40.460
to adjust crop varieties
in different regions.

27:40.460 --> 27:42.790
This way we can prevent future disasters.

27:44.840 --> 27:47.990
[Yan Millet Storage]

27:46.010 --> 27:46.810
However,

27:48.330 --> 27:49.810
this is just

27:49.940 --> 27:51.110
hastily written.

27:52.180 --> 27:54.210
It still needs to be adjusted

27:54.660 --> 27:56.660
during practical implementation.

28:03.280 --> 28:07.290
[Agricultural Distribution Map]

28:09.770 --> 28:11.660
In just a few months,

28:12.700 --> 28:16.140
you've accomplished what would
normally take two to three years.

28:16.140 --> 28:17.360
I feel truly ashamed

28:17.730 --> 28:19.330
for not visiting you sooner.

28:28.180 --> 28:29.010
I am...

28:29.900 --> 28:31.300
I am just a humble subject

28:31.490 --> 28:32.810
of this little use.

28:36.460 --> 28:37.320
Your Highness,

28:38.250 --> 28:39.650
how is His Majesty doing?

28:40.900 --> 28:42.300
Yang feared I would worry

28:43.090 --> 28:45.420
and didn't tell me about Mount Bei before.

28:46.010 --> 28:48.480
Otherwise, I wouldn't have asked Li
to deliver a message

28:48.480 --> 28:50.250
and trouble His Majesty at such a time.

28:50.250 --> 28:51.910
Please don't blame yourself.

28:53.200 --> 28:55.230
This is Physician Xiao from the palace.

28:55.230 --> 28:57.160
His medical skills are unmatched.

28:57.730 --> 28:58.860
His Majesty specifically ordered me

28:58.860 --> 29:00.260
to bring him to treat you.

29:01.730 --> 29:03.330
His Majesty also instructed

29:03.330 --> 29:05.460
that you should rest and recover well.

29:05.810 --> 29:06.750
Next year,

29:08.360 --> 29:10.340
when the Yan millet ripens in the fields,

29:10.340 --> 29:11.740
we'll go see it together.

29:17.730 --> 29:18.140
Sure.

29:20.110 --> 29:21.200
I will

29:23.490 --> 29:24.290
do my best.

29:42.900 --> 29:44.700
This person suffers
from an incurable disease.

29:44.700 --> 29:46.960
He was likely born with this affliction.

29:47.090 --> 29:48.490
Having not done anything until now,

29:48.490 --> 29:49.950
it's beyond medical help.

29:55.090 --> 29:55.900
The man inside

29:56.400 --> 29:58.660
is a benefactor to everyone
in Great Xia.

29:58.850 --> 30:01.910
Please, Physician Xiao,
help him live a little longer—

30:02.710 --> 30:04.440
even if just to see one harvest.

30:05.220 --> 30:05.620
I

30:06.550 --> 30:07.520
will do my best.

30:13.710 --> 30:16.460
[Agricultural Distribution Map]
[Yanwu Reserve Method]

30:23.450 --> 30:25.050
Don't worry, Your Highness.

30:26.300 --> 30:27.900
Since Physician Xiao is staying behind,

30:27.900 --> 30:29.810
he must have a way to save Mr. Cen.

30:34.940 --> 30:35.740
Let's hope so.

30:36.280 --> 30:42.870
[Agricultural Distribution Map 3]

30:48.490 --> 30:49.950
The men I promised to lend you

30:49.950 --> 30:51.610
will be waiting at the border.

30:52.100 --> 30:53.030
Though not many,

30:53.580 --> 30:55.180
they are all elite soldiers.

30:56.080 --> 30:57.280
After this succeeds,

30:58.040 --> 31:00.330
I hope our two nations
will remain allies forever

31:00.330 --> 31:01.730
and never wage war again.

31:05.570 --> 31:06.570
Are you so certain

31:07.180 --> 31:08.460
that I will be the victor?

31:08.460 --> 31:09.060
Of course.

31:10.180 --> 31:11.840
We are the same kind of person.

31:14.730 --> 31:17.420
You were forced
to become the prince of Yan State,

31:17.420 --> 31:17.980
while I

31:19.630 --> 31:21.960
reluctantly took the throne of Great Xia.

31:23.770 --> 31:26.100
Those around us commit all manner of evil,

31:26.860 --> 31:28.580
yet we have become

31:28.610 --> 31:30.520
puppets despised by thousands.

31:31.470 --> 31:33.400
I once almost wanted to give up too.

31:33.900 --> 31:36.250
But then I met someone very important.

31:37.890 --> 31:39.150
She made me understand

31:39.980 --> 31:40.840
what an emperor

31:41.880 --> 31:43.140
should truly do.

31:45.010 --> 31:47.530
As well as what
"heaven gave birth to the people"

31:47.530 --> 31:49.330
and ordained their fate" means.

31:50.770 --> 31:52.900
The way you Xia people speak in circles

31:53.140 --> 31:54.740
is beyond my understanding.

31:56.660 --> 31:58.120
But you are a good emperor.

31:59.700 --> 32:00.900
That's why I must win.

32:05.320 --> 32:06.450
And you must win too.

32:08.250 --> 32:09.580
People in our positions

32:10.530 --> 32:13.040
bear too many responsibilities and hopes.

32:14.690 --> 32:16.210
We cannot be villains.

32:18.780 --> 32:20.370
We may not become friends,

32:21.500 --> 32:23.430
but as long as I remain in Great Yan,

32:23.650 --> 32:24.910
Great Yan and Great Xia

32:26.390 --> 32:27.920
will never become enemies.

32:43.730 --> 32:45.990
Your Highness, someone's approaching.

32:46.770 --> 32:47.570
Hold on tight.

32:53.570 --> 32:54.310
Assassins!

32:54.330 --> 32:55.460
Protect our master!

33:17.370 --> 33:18.260
How insolent!

33:18.570 --> 33:20.670
How dare you defy the law
and attack people here?

33:20.670 --> 33:21.330
After them!

33:21.800 --> 33:22.580
Yes, Your Highness.

33:22.580 --> 33:23.310
My Lady.

33:24.530 --> 33:25.530
It's getting late

33:26.420 --> 33:27.690
and your carriage is damaged.

33:27.690 --> 33:28.970
May I offer you a ride?

33:38.130 --> 33:39.330
May I ask where

33:40.780 --> 33:42.310
your residence is, My Lady?

33:44.980 --> 33:47.180
Your Highness surely knows how to jest.

33:47.420 --> 33:49.420
Please escort me back to the palace.

33:50.490 --> 33:52.690
I happened to be here on business today.

33:54.320 --> 33:56.780
If anything were to happen
to Your Highness,

33:57.120 --> 33:58.780
His Majesty would be furious,

33:59.840 --> 34:02.020
and we wouldn't be able
to bear the consequences.

34:02.020 --> 34:03.400
At this point,

34:04.570 --> 34:05.580
Prince Duan,

34:06.660 --> 34:08.670
just be straightforward

34:09.090 --> 34:10.150
with your mockery.

34:10.929 --> 34:13.130
You're quite favored in the palace now,

34:13.639 --> 34:15.100
unmatched in prominence.

34:16.659 --> 34:18.370
I'm simply happy for you.

34:18.820 --> 34:20.679
My relationship with His Majesty

34:21.130 --> 34:22.590
could hardly be something

34:23.000 --> 34:24.980
you'd be happy about or anticipate.

34:24.980 --> 34:25.840
Unless perhaps

34:26.219 --> 34:27.639
if I were to win his true affection,

34:27.639 --> 34:29.100
I would be of greater value

34:29.100 --> 34:30.270
to Your Highness?

34:31.850 --> 34:33.750
After all, controlling me

34:34.330 --> 34:37.060
would give you better leverage
over His Majesty.

34:39.449 --> 34:40.330
Yu Wanyin.

34:43.040 --> 34:45.219
Do you realize what you're saying?

34:57.980 --> 34:58.720
Xiahou Dan.

34:59.780 --> 35:00.840
The person you said

35:01.230 --> 35:02.560
is very important to you

35:03.620 --> 35:05.220
is the Noble Consort, right?

35:08.010 --> 35:09.470
You must protect her well!

35:15.270 --> 35:16.620
Don't ever let her

35:18.260 --> 35:19.590
become another Shanyi.

35:19.920 --> 35:20.720
Your Majesty!

35:22.610 --> 35:23.410
Your Majesty.

35:27.610 --> 35:28.340
Your Majesty.

35:28.340 --> 35:28.870
Bad news.

35:29.710 --> 35:31.870
The officials who haven't taken sides
have fallen ill

35:31.870 --> 35:32.670
or died.

35:34.040 --> 35:35.570
He fears your spies

35:36.400 --> 35:38.130
and dares not leave the palace.

35:39.630 --> 35:41.720
He knows you intend to kill us,

35:42.670 --> 35:44.860
yet still sends me, a mere woman, to go

35:45.690 --> 35:46.950
just to demonstrate

35:47.770 --> 35:49.210
that he is a wise ruler.

35:50.110 --> 35:51.350
So you mean

35:52.550 --> 35:54.150
your trip outside the palace

35:54.640 --> 35:57.640
was His Majesty
sending you to win people over for him?

35:58.300 --> 35:59.900
And that his favor toward you

36:00.420 --> 36:01.680
isn't genuine either?

36:05.280 --> 36:06.740
That's quite a statement.

36:07.730 --> 36:09.440
Are you any different?

36:12.280 --> 36:13.810
Since I entered the palace,

36:14.350 --> 36:16.750
everyone claims their heart belongs to me,

36:17.460 --> 36:18.770
but deep down,

36:20.980 --> 36:22.860
isn't it all just manipulation

36:23.900 --> 36:24.960
and exploitation?

36:28.050 --> 36:28.980
You have a point.

36:31.360 --> 36:33.360
But for someone as clever as Wanyin,

36:34.610 --> 36:36.700
couldn't you find a way to refuse him?

36:38.090 --> 36:39.220
Why should I refuse?

36:40.420 --> 36:41.980
This is my best opportunity

36:41.980 --> 36:44.240
to scout an escape route from the palace.

36:45.400 --> 36:46.410
You want to

36:48.270 --> 36:48.900
escape?

36:49.620 --> 36:50.340
Your Majesty!

36:50.340 --> 36:51.010
Your Majesty!

36:51.010 --> 36:52.490
I've already sent the Imperial Guards
to rescue Her Highness.

36:52.490 --> 36:55.010
-Your Majesty, you can't go!
-She's in danger. I need to save her.

36:55.010 --> 36:55.300
Dan!

36:55.300 --> 36:56.010
-Let go!
-Your Majesty.

36:56.010 --> 36:56.380
Dan!

36:57.130 --> 36:57.980
You don't know martial arts.

36:57.980 --> 36:58.990
If you leave the palace,

36:58.990 --> 37:00.300
I fear I cannot protect you.

37:00.300 --> 37:01.840
What if something happens to her?

37:01.840 --> 37:02.350
Let go!

37:02.610 --> 37:03.170
-Your Majesty.
-Dan!

37:03.170 --> 37:03.680
Dan!

37:09.610 --> 37:10.290
Mr. Bei.

37:11.750 --> 37:12.390
You go.

37:14.210 --> 37:15.410
Only you can save her.

37:16.260 --> 37:16.860
